  "text": "The stability of the wide-angle transparent boundary conditions can be verified through a natural extension of our earlier analysis for the Schr\u00f6dinger-type Pad\u00e9-(2,0) approximant [CITATION_1] . Assume that the algorithm is implemented with exact arithmetic, and consider the representation of the exterior solution given by (14), namely",
